{"tid":452114,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[京阿尼]巴加的工作室","createTime":"2017-10-30T01:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T01:14:05.000Z","uid":33676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e18c4ef7cc78ea7b68f70bd1d9c5d629d551e9c1","tid":452114,"uid":33676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.moegirl.org/common/f/f9/Baja_no_Studio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.moegirl.org%2Fcommon%2Ff%2Ff9%2FBaja_no_Studio.jpg&h=7f210367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【摘要】<br />\n以京阿尼的吉祥物「巴佳」（バジャ）為主人公，以架空的動畫公司「KOHATA動畫工作室」為舞台，講述巴佳與朋友們的每一天。<br />\n2017年10月28日~29日舉辦的第3回京阿尼 &amp; Animation DO粉絲感謝祭入場券附帶的藍光光碟「私たちは、いま！！全集2017」將收錄本作品。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n監督：三好一郎<br />\n動畫檢查：黑田比呂子、松村元氣<br />\n色彩設計：宮田佳奈、竹田明代<br />\n特殊效果：三浦理奈<br />\n美術監督：落合翔子、細川直生<br />\n攝影監督：浦彰宏<br />\n3D監督：山本倫<br />\nCG演出：植田弘貴<br />\n音響監督：鶴岡陽太<br />\n動畫製作：京都動畫<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n巴佳：吉田舞妃<br />\n嘎嘎／吉：田村睦心<br />\n可可：田所梓<br />\n加奈子：金元壽子<br />\n石浦：金城大和<br />\n町村：星野充昭<br />\n敏夫：間島淳司<br />\n佐佐木／繪畫：代永翼<br />\n田島：種市桃子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kyotoanimation.co.jp/baja/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyotoanimation.co.jp%2Fbaja%2F&d=UtW9Xjt%2BaK%2Bs9a9qy0N3Pv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=97b1d689\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kyotoanimation.co.jp/baja/</a><br />\n<br />\nlink<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av15453233/?from=search&amp;seid=4020492778569548371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav15453233%2F%3Ffrom%3Dsearch%26seid%3D4020492778569548371&d=UtW9Xjt%2BaK%2Bs9a9qy0N3Pv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=94f470cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av15453233/?from=search&amp;seid=4020492778569548371</a>"},{"pid":"a3869ecab38e46f3da892a81d9afa0ed99c25dc1","tid":452114,"uid":33676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:14:05.000Z","msg":"因為係OVA形式出同埋係獨立作品<br />\n所以冇乜人知有出過<br />\n不過睇完之後覺得幾好睇<br />\n好吉卜力feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}